Shochiku Films

2
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:24,440
Good Morning

3
00:00:24,566 --> 00:00:31,071
Screenplay by
Kogo Noda and Yasujiro Ozu

4
00:00:31,197 --> 00:00:35,659
Produced by Shizuo Yamanouchi
